name: FingerPunk #002 (Eve)
description: This project pokes fun at the original CryptoPunks. The second FingerPunk to materialize was Eve. Before Adam was bounced from the garden of crypto he somehow managed to inject a single line of code into the system which created Eve. When Eve gained consciousness she quickly realized she was all alone in the garden. This made her sad, so she opened a portal to the Hicetnunc metaverse where she began her search for a collector to keep her company.
